#ROOM
Vnum     11330
Name     &rEarthborer Nest - South&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     Several large, leathery eggs are nestled in a bed of sand in the
corner. A low, wet squelching sound suggests that something is
moving just beyond the reach of your light.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11328
Desc      The main tunnel.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11303 10 11330
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11331
Name     &rEarthborer Tunnel - Deep&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The smooth walls of the tunnel begin to give way to jagged, 
volcanic rock once more. To the east, the tunnel opens into a large,
shadowy chamber.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11328
Desc      The slanted tunnel.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11332
Desc      A large, hollow cavern.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11303 10 11331
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11332
Name     &rThe Hollow Cavern&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     This large, naturally formed cavern is eerily silent. The ceiling
is lost in the darkness above, and the floor is littered with
pulverized stone. Tunnels lead away in every direction, forming a
confusing maze for the unwary.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11333
Desc      A jagged tunnel.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11334
Desc      A jagged tunnel.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11331
Desc      The deep tunnel.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11335
Desc      The end of the worm tunnels.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11303 10 11332
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11333
Name     &rThe Jagged Cul-de-sac - North&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     This small tunnel ends abruptly in a wall of solid obsidian.
Several deep grooves are carved into the rock, as if a massive
creature tried to burrow through and failed.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11332
Desc      The hollow cavern.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11303 10 11333
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11334
Name     &rThe Jagged Cul-de-sac - South&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A pile of bleached white bones lies in the center of this small
alcove. Among them, you spot the remains of an unfortunate orcish
scout who wandered too deep into the worm territory.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11332
Desc      The hollow cavern.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11303 10 11334
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11335
Name     &rTunnel's End&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The worm tunnels end here. A narrow fissure leads through the
back wall, offering a glimpse into the Shadow Council sanctum beyond.
The air smells of ozone and dark magic.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11332
Desc      The hollow cavern.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11336
Desc      The Shadow Council Sanctum.~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11336
Name     &MThe Shadow Council Sanctum - Entry&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     This massive chamber has been converted into a fortified camp for
the Shadow Council. Tents made of dark leather are arranged around
a central dais, and crates of magical supplies are stacked high
against the walls.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11321
Desc      The southern corridor.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11337
Desc      The central sanctum area.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11335
Desc      The worm tunnels.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11306 1 11336
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11337
Name     &MThe Shadow Council Sanctum - Center&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A large stone dais sits in the center of the room, upon which a
pool of swirling, purple energy has been summoned. Orcish mages
stand around it, maintaining the portal with constant incantations.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11336
Desc      The sanctum entry.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11338
Desc      A path to the lower depths.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11339
Desc      The deep sanctum.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11340
Desc      A small storage area.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11306 1 11337
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11338
Name     &MThe descent to the Lower Depths&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A wide set of stairs has been carved into the rock, leading down
toward the very bottom of the chasm. The sound of a violent, fiery
clash echoes from below.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11337
Desc      The central sanctum.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction down~
ToRoom    11342
Desc      The Fiery Descent.~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11339
Name     &MThe Deep Sanctum&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The walls here are covered in demonic scripts that seem to pulse
with their own internal light. This is the inner circle of the
outpost, where the most powerful warlocks congregate.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11337
Desc      The central sanctum.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11341
Desc      Jergosh the Invoker's Altar.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11306 1 11339
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11340
Name     &MSanctum Storage Area&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     Piles of iron ingots, bundles of staves, and sacks of sulfur are
organized neatly here. It seems the Shadow Council is preparing
for a long stay beneath Orgrimmar.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11337
Desc      The central sanctum.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset O 0 11310 10 11340
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11341
Name     &MJergosh the Invoker's Altar&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A massive obsidian altar dominates the southern wall, dripping
with a viscous, green liquid. Jergosh the Invoker stands before it,
clutching a staff of dark iron and screaming commands at the 
twisting shadows that dance around him.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11339
Desc      The deep sanctum.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11306 1 11341
  Reset G 1 11305 1
  Reset G 1 11307 1
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11342
Name     &RThe Fiery Descent&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The stairs end in a wide, circular platform suspended over a 
bottomless pit of roiling magma. The heat here is lethal, and only
the presence of powerful demonic magic keeps the platform from 
melting into the depths.
~
#EXIT
Direction up~
ToRoom    11338
Desc      The descent stairs.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11343
Desc      Taragaman's Maw.~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11343
Name     &RTaragaman's Maw&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     This is the lowest point of Ragefire Chasm. A massive bridge of
twisted, dark iron crosses the lava pit, leading to a central 
throne where the demon Taragaman the Hungerer stands sentinel. 
The air is screaming with the sound of escaping steam and the
demon's own guttural roars.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11342
Desc      The Fiery Descent.~
